<p class="MsoNormal"><b><span style="font-family:&quot;Palatino Linotype&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;">By&nbsp;Jeremy Diamond, CNN</span></b><o:p></o:p></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-family:&quot;Palatino Linotype&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;"><br>
<span style="background:yellow;mso-highlight:yellow">Two years before the housing market collapsed in 2008 and millions of Americans lost their homes, Donald Trump said he was hoping for a crash.</span></span><o:p></o:p></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Palatino Linotype&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;"><br>
