<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-family:&quot;Palatino Linotype&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;">The U.S. housing bubble burst two years later, triggering the stock market crash of 2008 that plunged the U.S. economy into a deep recession, leaving millions of Americans unemployed.</span><o:p></o:p></p>
