 underscore the challenges the billionaire and presumptive Republican nominee will increasingly face in the general election as comments from his life before politics return to haunt him.</span><o:p></o:p></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-family:&quot;Palatino Linotype&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;"><br>
